<p>将如下代码保存至名为app.psgi的文件中：</p>

<pre class="brush: pl; class-name: 'highlight'; toolbar: false; gutter: false">
#!/usr/bin/perl
use strict;
use warnings;

# Serve static files from document root with a directory index
# app.psgi
use Plack::App::Directory;
my $app = Plack::App::Directory-&gt;new({ 
                root =&gt; &quot;/path/to/htdocs&quot; 
            })-&gt;to_app;
</pre>


<p>Then run</p>

<pre class="brush: pl; class-name: 'highlight'; toolbar: false; gutter: false">
&gt; plackup
&gt; Accepting connections at http://0:5000/
</pre>

